---
title: Honey & Chipotle-Glazed Meatballs with Garlic-Spinach Rice & Sweetcorn Salsa
description: Give pork meatballs a dash of flair with a glaze of chipotle sauce and sweet honey for a melding of robust flavours. Then, don’t
stop there. Ramp up your dish with baby spinach tossed around with aromatic garlic rice. This one’s an exciting ride from start to
finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-chipotle-glazed-meatballs-7f9be356.jpg
